Module fr.cyu

Package C.Languages

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CLanguage
    The CLanguage class provides methods to compile and execute C language programs.
    JavaLanguage
    The JavaLanguage class provides methods to compile and execute Java programs.
    JsLanguage
    The JsLanguage class provides methods to execute JavaScript programs.
    Language
    The Language class provides methods to execute programs and handle input/output streams.
    LanguageFactory
    The LanguageFactory class is used to automatically assign a language to a given file by looking at its extension.
    PHPLanguage
    The PHPLanguage class provides methods to execute PHP programs.
    PythonLanguage
    The PythonLanguage class provides methods to execute Python programs.
